<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>

    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>
        Your order has been received!<br>
        Thank you for your trust.
    </p>

    <h3>Order Details :</h3>

    <ul>
        <li>Total : {{ order.totalPrice }} €</li>
        <li>Shipping Cost : {{ order.city.shippingCost }} €</li>
        <li>Total to Pay : {{ order.totalPrice + order.city.shippingCost }} €</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        You will be contacted shortly for delivery.
    </p>

    <br>
    <p>Thank you.</p>
</body>
</html>